# Build binaries are Git LFS-tracked (see .gitattributes), NOT ignored: they must
# be committable to LFS for the air-gapped USB transfer (transfer/Export-Transfer
# copies the LFS CAS). On the public dev leg the real binaries are simply absent
# (pointer-only); the internal leg carries them via USB.
# DO NOT re-add blanket binaries/ or tools/ ignores -- that shadows the LFS rules
# and silently drops the binaries from `git add` (the gitignore-shadows-LFS bug).

# Credentials
*.env
secrets.json
# Real Packer/Terraform secret var-files (example.pkrvars.hcl IS committed)
*.auto.pkrvars.hcl
secret.pkrvars.hcl
*.auto.tfvars
terraform.tfvars
# Terraform state + local dirs
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*

# Logs
*.log
*.log.old

# Temp files
*.tmp
~$*

# Agent / workflow logs
agent-logs/

# OS
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
